data.description: Located in the exclusive and peaceful community of Black Rail Ridge, this one-story Mayfair home is a testament to exquisite craftsmanship and meticulous attention to detail. As you step through the entryway turret, you'll be captivated by the sheer elegance and charm that defines this residence.  The interior appointments of this home envelop you in a realm of serene luxury. Recently remodeled, the spa-like master bath is a testament to modern comfort and indulgence, ensuring that every moment spent here is a soothing retreat from the world outside. Whether you're whipping up family dinners or hosting grand gatherings, you'll find immense pleasure in the showcase island kitchen. Adorned with a pristine slab of granite countertops, rich stain-grade Beech cabinetry, and an impressive array of state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances, it's the heart of this home where culinary dreams come to life. Step outside to discover the expansive and tranquil backyard, a haven of relaxation. With a recently constructed front patio, you can savor the gentle Western breezes and catch fleeting glimpses of the ocean, creating an outdoor paradise perfect for unwinding or entertaining. Located just a mere one and a half miles from the beach, this property offers easy access to a wealth of attractions. From first-class shopping to luxury cinemas, five-star-rated hotels, and highly acclaimed schools, you'll enjoy a lifestyle that seamlessly blends convenience and sophistication.
